          "type": "testimonials_slide",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "slide_text": "“These hearing aids from Ceretone seem to be very high quality with many different adjustments and features. The adjustments are also easy to use and understand compared to other OTC hearing aids I have tried in the past. My favorite feature of these is that they are very small and don’t catch wind and vibration from driving compared to other hearing aids I have used in the past.”",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/71_CtkPLrwL._SY1000.jpg",
            "slide_name": "David K.",
            "slide_position": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonials_slide_nPxAzc": {
          "type": "testimonials_slide",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "slide_text": "“The Ceretone Core One Pro hearing aids are the future of hearing aids. They are incredibly small and fit in your ear canals. The only thing visible is the tiny clear removal thread.”",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/61ir70ZlgjL._SY1000.jpg",
            "slide_name": "Eleanor E.",
            "slide_position": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonials_slide_MetD6Q": {
          "type": "testimonials_slide",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "slide_text": "“This one was so easy to set up and use, didn’t even need help. I can turn the TV way down now and still hear everything. Super happy I found this—works great and don’t break the bank!”",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1753856237__1753856232420-mvimg_20250724_162004__original.avif",
            "slide_name": "Carol D.",
            "slide_position": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonials_slide_RXnyKH": {
          "type": "testimonials_slide",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "slide_text": "“I got this hearing aid set for my dad. He is so impressed with them. The noise canceling and wind noise management work really well. He doesn't get the whistling as much as he has gotten with other aids, and is very rare with these.”",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ZtQOSlGHb33kr5iPKYURaQ.jpg",
            "slide_name": "Melisaa M.",
